description:
LoginRadius ASP.NET Customer Registration wrapper provides access to LoginRadius Identity Management Platform API.

LoginRadius is an Identity Management Platform that simplifies user registration while securing data. LoginRadius Platform simplifies and secures your user registration process, increases conversion with Social Login that combines 30 major social platforms, and offers a full solution with Traditional User Registration. You can gather a wealth of user profile data from Social Login or Traditional User Registration.

LoginRadius centralizes it all in one place, making it easy to manage and access. Easily integrate LoginRadius with all of your third-party applications, like MailChimp, Google Analytics, Livefyre and many more, making it easy to utilize the data you are capturing.
summary: LoginRadius manages your registration process, keeps your customer data secure. LoginRadius User Registration and Social Login solutions work seamlessly together for a simplified registration system.
title: LoginRadius - User Registration SDK
